      "title": "The third reading of the budget is also standard",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The third reading of the Appropriation (Amendment) Bill to amend the Appropriation Act No. 30 of 2021 was passed in Parliament today (02) without a vote.",
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe, as the Minister of Finance, Economic Stabilization and National Policy Affairs, delivered the opening speech of the second reading of the Appropriation (Amendment) Bill to amend the Appropriation Act No. 30 of 2021 in the Parliament on August 30, after which the Appropriation (Amendment) Acts The debate on the second reading of the draft was held last August 31, September 01 and today."
      ],
